== Slovak ==
=== Etymology ===
The word is derived from ''[[Slavs]]'', which in turn could come from '''[[slovo#Slovak|slovo]]'''&mdash;''word'' (i.e. those whose language we can understand) or from ''slo/sla-'' (water-, i.e. "people from the water"). 

